title: Bassett and Walker International, Inc. Recall Beef Products Produced Without Benefit of Import Inspection
summary: WASHINGTON, July 7, 2015 Bassett & Walker International, Inc., a Toronto, Canada, establishment, is recalling approximately 1,540 pounds of beef lip products produced in Australia that were not presented at the U.S. point of entry for inspection, the U.S. Department of Agricultures Food Safety and...
